        <title>Human Rights Information Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To promote human rights, democracy, and the rule of law by providing a process for executive agencies for declassifying on an expedited basis and disclosing certain documents relating to human rights abuses in countries other than the United States.</title>
